<div class="span4">
  <h2>HCLC Champion</h2>
  <p>The 2014 Hoosier Crossroad Lacrosse Conference (HCLC) championship was awarded to the Zionsville Eagles with their 9-5 win against Fishers on Wednesday April 30th. This is the second straight championship for head coach Matt Garvey and the Zionsville Eagles. The Eagles won their HCLC championship with an undefeated conference record of 4-0 and this is the second straight season Zionsville has earned the HCLC Championship with an undefeated conference record. Zionsville is a perfect 8-0 in conference play dating back to 2013. Congratulations to the Zionsville Eagles on their 2014 HCLC championship!</p>
  <p><a class="btn" href="leagueuploads/Hoosier_Crossroads_Lacrosse_Conference_2014_Champion.pdf">View details &raquo;</a></p>
